media
=====

Getting Started
---------------

1. Downloading the App
----------------------

Navigate to the directory where the media app will live.

**Terminal:**

*In macOS, it is recommended to start in the user's `Applications` folder*

```cd ~/Applications

Download the media repository to the local media directory.

**Terminal:**

*The following step requires [Git](https://git-scm.com)*

```git clone https://github.com/quantastical/media

Verify that the repository was downloaded properly.

**Terminal:**

```open README

2. Updating the App
-------------------

Update the local media directory with the latest changes in the repository.

**Terminal:**

*The following step requires [Git](https://www.git-scm.com)*

```cd ~/Applications/media
```git pull

3. Starting the App
-------------------

**Terminal:**

*The following step requires [NodeJS](https://www.nodejs.org)*

```cd ~/Applications/media
```node media